                        <additions>
                            <list>
                                <item xml:id="a1">
                                    <locus target="#172"/>
                                    <desc type="MagicFormula"><title type="work" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5696MagicPrayer">Rampart of the Cross (General record)</title></desc>
                                    <q xml:lang="gez">
                                        በዝንቱ፡ ሐፁረ፡ መስቀል፡ እግዚኦ፡ ሀበኒ፡ ሞገሰ፡ ወግርማ፡ ዘረከበት፡ እሌኒ፡ ንግሥት፡<gap reason="ellipsis"/>
                                    </q>
                                </item>
                                
                                <item xml:id="a2">
                                    <locus from="172v"/>
                                    <desc type="ProtectivePrayer">
                                        <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/X4SBAXAT"><seg type="book"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Loefgren1974Katalog"/><title level="m">Katalog über die äthiopischen Handschriften in der Universitätsbibliothek Uppsala, Sowie Anhänge über äthiopische Handschriften in anderen Bibliotheken und in Privatbesitz in Schweden</title><title level="s">Acta Bibliothecae R. Universitatis Upsaliensis</title><author><t:forename xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Oscar</t:forename><t:surname xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Löfgren</t:surname></author><pubPlace>Uppsala</pubPlace><publisher>Almqvist &amp; Wiksell</publisher><date>1974</date><series><t:title xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" level="s">Acta Bibliothecae R. Universitatis Upsaliensis</t:title><t:biblScope xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" unit="volume">18</t:biblScope></series><biblScope unit="volume">18</biblScope><citedRange unit="page">41</citedRange></bibl>
                                        calls it a "litany to Jesus Christ" ("<foreign xml:lang="de">Litanei an Jesus Christus</foreign>")
                                        and notes that it contains a repeated <foreign xml:id="gez">ተማኅፀንኩ፡ </foreign>.
                                        He points to <ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3071RepCh351">Hymn to Jesus Christ</ref>,
                                         <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BLorient617#ms_i3">No item: BLorient617, could not check for ms_i3</ref>, and
                                        <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BNFet362#ms_i2">No item: BNFet362, could not check for ms_i2</ref>
                                        as parallels.
                                    </desc>
                                    <q xml:lang="gez">
                                        ኦእግዚእየ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ዘኩሉ፡ ትእኅዝ፡ ተማኅፀንኩ፡ በእኅዘትከ፡ በመጣብኅ፡ ወበአብትር፡ 
                                        ወበእስረትከ፡ በኀብል፡ ወበሕማዬከ፡ ድኅሪተ፡ ከመ፡ ሠራዊ፡<gap reason="ellipsis"/>
                                    </q>
                                </item>
                                                              
                                <item xml:id="e1">
                                    <desc>One secondary owner, mentioned in
                                        supplications, is <persName role="owner" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS14770AsrataMaryam">ʾAsrāta Māryām</persName>.</desc>
                                    <q xml:lang="gez"/>
                                </item>
                            </list>
                        </additions>
                        
                        
